<br>
The argument of well they don't spec in evocation is not true, as many a druid does, the same exact way many magician's are either evocation OR conjuration.<br>
<br>
 For a magician the case can be made for either, as it can for the Druid class.<br>
<br>
 A druid with PoTc has 6 mana per tick self regen, and with mask of the stalker an additional 3 more for 9 per tick.<br>
<br>
With what we are seeing with the proposed PoP upgrade those numbers on mana regen go 8 and 4, for 12 mana per tick,  and that is even better than the crrent KEI.<br>
<br>
On top of that their current spells STACK with KEI, and I would think the new ones would also stack with KEI or the new C4 spell.<br>
<br>
So a the loss of mana efficency for a druid spec'd in alteration is nulified by their self only mana regen buffs, WAY more than our 3 mana per tick we get.<br>
<br>
So their nuking effiency if alt spec'd is more than offset by their self mana regen buffs, and as Druids can get SCF3 as well. They could easily go evocation, and still heal do to their mana regen.<br>
<br>
Before I am accussed of Druid bashing or envy, I want to point out. I was am in favor of their new 3000 point heal, and in fact, the way it works now, their AAXP skills on healing do not effect it and they should.<br>
<br>
I also feel that with the healing upgrades Magician's should out nuke Druids. Maybe on a DD scale we are even, but our last bolt should be superior to their best DD spell.<br>
<br>
Why anyone would disagree with that is amazing. Druids are an amazing class, with a ton of abilites, and the new healing just raised that bar a lot higher.<br>
<br>
So I want our best nuke to out damage them. I play a magician, I want us to shine agin in that area, and be second to only wizards.<br>
<br>
We lost ground in the nuking arena, and our best magic based nuke is a worse ration and does less damage than the best Enchanter magic based nuke.<br>
<br>
Even with the upgraded mana cost it still is a better ration than the Magician's. <br>
<br>
I want the slide to stop, and be reversed. Hell ya I am passionate about this issue. Too many people who post here, love to cheer when others are upgraded over ourselves, and than rant and flame those of us that say. WAIT A MINUTE why the hell are others passing us in this ability when there prime abilities are upgraded ALONG with their nukes?<br>
<br>
Druids=jack of all trades and get a huge healing boost, and nuke upgrades.<br>
<br>
Enchanters=Crowd control/buffing/de-buffing/ and now has a superior mana/damage ratio magic based nuke than magician's.<br>
<br>
We point this out, and some call us whiners, because we point out we are losing ground, and want the trend STOPPED. For once some of you playing a magician that say this is whining, please point out to me WHEN our last upgrade was THAT DIDN'T effect other classes.<br>
<br>
Pets Upgrades= all pet classes.<br>
<br>
Focus Items= In game AND we could give to others. Nice but not magician only upgrade.<br>
<br>
